import React from 'react';
import { Header, Icon, Segment, Grid, Embed, Modal, Button, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import Vikings from '../Video/Vikings.mp4';
import Got from '../Video/got.mp4';
import ReactPlayer from 'react-player'


const HeaderPart = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Grid columns="equal" inverted>
                <Grid.Row textAlign='right'>
                    <Grid.Column>
                        <Segment color='red' inverted>
                            <ReactPlayer url={Vikings}
                                //autoPlay
                                //playing
                                loop
                                width='100%'
                                controls
                                left="50%"
                            />
                        </Segment>
                    </Grid.Column>
                    <Grid.Column>
                        <Segment color='red' inverted>
                            <Modal trigger={<Button>Show Modal</Button>}>
                                {/* <Modal.Header>Select a Photo</Modal.Header> */}
                                <Modal.Content>
                                    <Modal.Description>
                                        <Segment color='red' inverted>
                                            <ReactPlayer url={Vikings}
                                                //autoPlay
                                                //playing
                                                loop
                                                width='100%'
                                                controls
                                                left="50%"
                                            />
                                        </Segment>
                                    </Modal.Description>
                                </Modal.Content>
                            </Modal>
                        </Segment>
                    </Grid.Column>
                </Grid.Row>
            </Grid>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default HeaderPart;
